song_lyrics: Āj Vasant pratham din āvyo, sahu janne sukhkārī;
Chhūṭī lāj ājathī sajanī, ūpajyo ānand bhārī... ° 1
Van taru latā velī premātur, nav pallav thaī sārī;
Kunj kunj prati kokilā sundar, bolat vasant khumārī... ° 2
Shrī Ghanshyām piyā sang ramavā, ati ātur Vrajnārī;
Ango ang fūlī sahu abaḷā, nautam neh vadhārī... ° 3
Rachyo manorath ramavā sāru, thaī taruṇī sahu tyārī;
Tan man dhan Ghanshyām chhabī par, Premānand balihārī... ° 4
title: Āj Vasant pratham din āvyo
